{"tid":346304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[8月4號]天文台在上午6時20分發出黃色暴雨警告信號","createTime":"2017-08-03T22:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T23:09:26.000Z","uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0f66ba34e1bcbd82ed32e90ee6011efebc0cbf","tid":346304,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/a3Glu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Fa3Glu.jpg&h=94eb2589&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bfcb2506cbdfbfdfd166d7e2d0c2e2bca6bacaf","tid":346304,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:30:35.000Z","msg":"香港天文台在上午6時20分發出之有關黃色暴雨警告信號的特別報告：<br />\n<br />\n暴雨警告信號現時為黃色，表示香港廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每小時雨量超過30毫米的大雨，且雨勢可能持續。<br />\n<br />\n一些低窪地帶及排水欠佳的地區會出現水淹。可能受大雨及水浸影響之市民應採取適當的預防措施，以防止可能引致的損失。<br />\n<br />\n大雨可能引致山洪暴發，市民應遠離河道。可能受河道氾濫影響之市民應採取適當的預防措施，以避免損失。<br />\n<br />\n請留意電台或電視台廣播有關交通情況及其他有關暴雨消息之報告。"},{"pid":"8c68935766716e2fe8699836411700deafd6db71","tid":346304,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:31:13.000Z","msg":"我呢邊一滴都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9948accd223d3020955ec813cf2d7584aae7c417","tid":346304,"uid":27334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我呢邊一滴都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n癡撚線公司"},{"pid":"7a0de73a277dcf830f3ab27975c96bb328993210","tid":346304,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我呢邊一滴都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭先電話彈個message出黎仲以為bug"},{"pid":"06a6cd1e9259d43b4ac0e6aef459bd926c4ada35","tid":346304,"uid":14636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我呢邊一滴都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe too"},{"pid":"ea7404c831564990d7dab916a7b223d120f3f9b4","tid":346304,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:33:50.000Z","msg":"睇圖雨雲應該係西南面上緊黎"},{"pid":"139cb200e7d54eacbbc7b470e51c3d2807295f6e","tid":346304,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我呢邊一滴都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMe too</blockquote><br />\n機場落兩滴水就黃雨，市區就落狗屎水浸先黃雨"},{"pid":"602cb58ac494d3c3f66d22d9c3583a08d09f8e2b","tid":346304,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:51:26.000Z","msg":"個天好似黑左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f34abae869b3ea74cb6fbc25c3820c6c3b18d6","tid":346304,"uid":42910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T22:54:44.000Z","msg":"好大霧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56d8355e11117edc48ebe3aab94a3ec2e5f17e4","tid":346304,"uid":41130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T23:06:15.000Z","msg":"開始有雨了"},{"pid":"fe5fcee1eb154f2258ed9c12b2c79750fa9e9a96","tid":346304,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T23:07:57.000Z","msg":"醒目啦打埋日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc6c9256da871209d31a7f3a5753add77d7a581","tid":346304,"uid":45494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T23:09:26.000Z","msg":"其實呢D先係真正既警告信號呀嘛屌<br />\n梗係預早提你出門會落雨<br />\n唔係落到狗屎先話會落雨<img src=\"/assets/f